vote.title: Receive the report of the Ad Hoc City Council Canvassing Committee and adopt a resolution and order accepting the canvassing committee's report declaring the amended results of the Saturday, May 3, 2025 general election for Place 6 based on the manual recount, per Texas Election Code 213.033 - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
